import { Box, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import { Stack } from '@mui/system'
import React from 'react'

const Products = () => {
  return (
    <Box>
      <Typography variant='h6' mt={2} component='div' color='white' mx={1}>
        Products
      </Typography>
      <Stack direction='row' spacing={2} color='white'>
        <Typography mx={2} variant='body1'>
        Pin92 
        </Typography>
      
        <Typography mx={0}>
        Property051
        </Typography>
        <Typography mx={0}>
         Rudn Enclave 
        </Typography>
       


      </Stack>
    </Box>
  )
}

export default Products
